Quantico will not fail to impress you. The show revolves around the life of 7 FBI recruits at the FBI Academy in Quantico in the state of Virginia. The protagonist, Alex Parrish takes you on a roller coaster ride as she ventures out to find the person who has framed her for committing a terrorist attack (a bomb blast) which she has nothing to do with. There are frequent flashbacks and the show is set in 2 time zones. The first one being at the start of their recruitment, while the other deals with 9 months post recruitment when the blast has occurred. Watch the show and the suspense itself will grip you. The pilot episode received a total of 7 million views in the US and has been one of ABC's successful pilot episodes of all time. Watch it.